<HEAD>Lufthansa Announces Stock Issue To Raise $478 Million</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BONN, West Germany (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Lufthansa, West Germany's national
airline, on Wednesday announced plans to raise $478 million by
issuing new shares at a discount to prepare for an expected increase
in air travel in the 1990s.
